story: Soon after Daenerys Targaryen was hungry for revenge and chased down Margaery Tyrell. At the Autumnal Equinox in Bear Island,  our hero met Daenerys Targaryen again, and they fought in the final battle. Margaery Tyrell won the duel and took the life of the villain. At the Middle Of the Night in The Trident, Margaery Tyrell was finally safe, and celebrated with Lyanna Stark by organizing a concert.
